### ====================================
### H AND M SUPERMARKET API TESTS
### ====================================

### 1. Check server status
GET http://localhost:5000/

### ====================================
### AUTHENTICATION
### ====================================

### 2. Register a new user
# @name register
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Hassan Sharif",
    "email": "hassan@example.com",
    "password": "123456"
}

### 3. Login
# @name login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "hassan@example.com",
    "password": "123456"
}

### Save token for later requests
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 4. Get user profile (requires token)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Update user profile
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Hassan Sharif Ahmed",
    "address": [{
        "street": "KG 123 St",
        "city": "Kigali",
        "phone": "+250788123456"
    }]
}

### ====================================
### PRODUCTS
### ====================================

### 6. Get all products
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products

### 7. Get products with filters
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products?category=Fruits&featured=true&sort=price-asc&page=1&limit=5

### 8. Search products
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products?search=apple

### 9. Create a new product (admin only - you need to be admin)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Fresh Apples",
    "description": "Crisp and sweet apples from local farms",
    "price": 3000,
    "category": "Fruits",
    "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560806887-1e4cd0b6cbd6",
    "stock": 50,
    "unit": "kg",
    "featured": true,
    "discount": 0
}

### ====================================
### ORDERS
### ====================================

### 10. Create an order (requires token)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "orderItems": [
        {
            "product": "PRODUCT_ID_HERE",
            "quantity": 2
        }
    ],
    "shippingAddress": {
        "street": "KG 123 St",
        "city": "Kigali",
        "phone": "+250788123456"
    },
    "paymentMethod": "stripe"
}

### 11. Get user's orders
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders/myorders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ====================================
### PAYMENTS
### ====================================

### 12. Create payment intent (requires token)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/payments/create-payment-intent
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "items": [
        {
            "_id": "PRODUCT_ID_HERE",
            "price": 3000,
            "quantity": 2
        }
    ],
    "shippingAddress": {
        "street": "KG 123 St",
        "city": "Kigali",
        "phone": "+250788123456"
    }
}